channel.title: Calling a void
channel.description:
Ok, well I went to call my void when this happened :(
[code]client.java:12845: HintIcon(int,int) in client cannot be applied to () HintIcon(); ^[/code]
How could I call upon it in the correct way?

herd u were r4ring and got rep reset

Very stupid, we should at least get a warning or something…[/quote]your 0 rep is hot. Really, jealous
